  <summary date="2018-01-16T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Broadband Conduit Deployment Act of 2018

This bill directs the Department of Transportation to require states to evaluate the need to install broadband conduit in any project to construct a new highway or additional lane or paved shoulder for an existing highway that is begun after the enactment of this bill and that receives funding under the federal-aid highway program.</summary>
